            <thetext>This enhancement allows filters to be specified to qx.log.Logger at runtime which control what log messages got to what Appenders; the filters are based on a regular expression matched against the class name of the object which is making the log.

This patch also adds &quot;trace&quot; as a seperate logging level so that each individual appender can decide whether to pass stack information on.

If no filters are applied, then the behaviour is unchanged from previous versions.

https://github.com/qooxdoo/qooxdoo/pull/152</thetext>
